# Live Band / Jam Session Feature Integration

Integrate real-time multiplayer jam sessions from the [airjam-jam-export](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/airjam-jam-export) folder into the existing AirPlay project. Players can host/join rooms via 6-char codes and play piano or drums together over WebSocket.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend — Session Server
#### [NEW] [session_server.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/session_server.py)
- Copy [session_server.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/airjam-jam-export/session_server.py) directly to project root (it's standalone)
- FastAPI app on **port 8502**: `POST /create_room` + `GET /ws/{room_id}/{player_id}`
- Broadcasts note messages to all other clients in the same room

